channel.title: Give me something to do
channel.description:
Ok im really bored and i dont know what to do.. i dont want to train PC anymore on runescape and have nothing better to do untell lost comes on at 9..
any game suggestions 3d text i dun care as long as i dont have to download it..
I already play.. www.torncity.com (over a year might quit cuz i got jacked of 5Mil which took me a year to get) www.Finalearth.com (isnt working ATM server down) www.tycoononline.nu (not waisting my login turns already went on 2 times today) www.tribalwars.net (cant really do anything untell buildings are done) www.cyber-wars.com (used my turns)
Prolly missing something there but yeah just dont tell me any of those games.
